{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 210239, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "强基才是人上人啊", "timestamp": 1596508562, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210240, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "强基又不能转专业，有没有自带名额不重要吧", "timestamp": 1596508606, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210244, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 强基不是本硕博贯通培养吗，所以是不是学校把大部分保研名额优先保证给强基了", "timestamp": 1596508682, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210247, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "强基目前的说法是没有自带名额", "timestamp": 1596508757, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210248, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 可能，但强基并没有限制出国，只是不能转专业了而已", "timestamp": 1596508763, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210251, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "取消自带名额据说是邱宝上台后推进的全校性质的政策", "timestamp": 1596508787, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210255, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 谁说贯通培养就有自带名额啊？", "timestamp": 1596508841, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210257, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以管它什么院系都统统取消", "timestamp": 1596508840, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210260, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 啊这，邱宝是觉得这届本科生质量不行，扩大考研名额，还是准备国际化，多招国际生啊", "timestamp": 1596508874, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210265, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 为了“公平”吧", "timestamp": 1596508909, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210266, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 邱宝上台几年了，在7字班入学前就说要取消自带名额了", "timestamp": 1596508932, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210269, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 真要公平他设什么学堂班啊。。。。", "timestamp": 1596509000, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210277, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 学堂班和公平与否又有什么关系呢？", "timestamp": 1596509088, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210282, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 学堂班是教育部给钱", "timestamp": 1596509183, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210287, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 如果认为学堂班有自带名额是不公平，那学堂班有师资和各种资金资源支持也说不上公平吧", "timestamp": 1596509268, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210310, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 学堂班从来也没有过自带名额，洞主知道的还是太少了", "timestamp": 1596509511, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210311, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 学堂班的资金来自教育部“基础学科拔尖人才培养计划”，可以看做挂靠在清华下面但受清华管辖不多的一个机构", "timestamp": 1596509512, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210322, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 啊这，钱班和数理基科不算学堂班吗", "timestamp": 1596509567, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210326, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 啊这，你这言论把我逗乐了", "timestamp": 1596509597, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210331, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 建议查查学堂班是干啥的，基科能成学堂班做梦都能笑醒", "timestamp": 1596509625, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210347, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/WnzhYg0_1dLLwKb8LXQiog\n公众号推送把这两个班都算在学堂计划里啊，怎么了有问题吗", "timestamp": 1596509709, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210353, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 基科不是学堂班，学堂班只有“清华学堂物理班”，不是行政班", "timestamp": 1596509828, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210363, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: well，那我的表述可能有问题，但这并不重要，我想表达的意思是如果只是为了公平，“钱班”“数理基科班”这样的试点班级就没有存在的必要。既然是试点，取消一部分优惠条件肯定是有其他原因的", "timestamp": 1596509987, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210365, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那你去学堂计划官网上看一下介绍，这推送写的有些问题", "timestamp": 1596510009, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210382, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 所以数理基科取消保研是因为办了个试点班级然后现在发现效果不好/大佬不背书了，所以逐步降级了吗", "timestamp": 1596510270, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210441, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不一定，这个说法很难解释钱班也取消自带名额", "timestamp": 1596511020, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210449, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 有可能是为了公平，毕竟那些试点班级是邱宝上台前搞的……", "timestamp": 1596511072, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210455, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 基科从2000左右开始，一开始效果是非常好的，培养了一票在美国top任教的学生，但后来数学系物理系闹翻了，基科就变成了“物理基科”，培养的人才质量开始有所下降", "timestamp": 1596511100, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210458, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 变成物理基科之后真正想搞学术就直接留在物理系了，也不会去基科。基科就从培养学术人才的基地逐渐变成了往其他方向转的跳板", "timestamp": 1596511165, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210462, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 2000年左右的基科就和现在的姚班差不多，所以呀各位，还是要用发展的眼光看问题", "timestamp": 1596511227, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210539, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 学堂班是教育部政策“拔尖计划”，钱班、姚班和数理化生学堂班都在其列。学校不可能敢取消这些班级。\n基科是实验班性质的，有历史原因带来的自带保研，类似于新雅的优惠。学校也没必要取消这样的特色班级。\n所以你上面说的“师资和各种资金资源支持”其实不可能取消的。（说实话，有的学堂班也不比普通学生多多少资源）\n但是自带保研的取消是学校政策，好像是想把保研政策统一化之类的想法。", "timestamp": 1596512108, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210570, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 那新雅的优惠为什么留下来了呢", "timestamp": 1596512522, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210719, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 38079, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 目前不清楚，我以为新雅的自带保研也取消了来着，今天看树洞才知道，有点惊诧", "timestamp": 1596514519, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 11, "pid": 38079, "reply": 33, "tag": null, "text": "#38076\n所以跨学科的学堂班为何集体取消自带名额，是为了给强基让路吗？", "timestamp": 1596508518, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782600, "url": "", "vote": {}}}